    public class podHomeBean.DecoratedPodcastBean

    Bean to store information about a single podcast. Used by main page to display and to store which podcast is to be Revised or Deleted.

      • getNewWindow

        public String getNewWindow()
        Returns a value to determine if file should be opened in same window or a new one. _self means open in same window, _blank means open in a new window. If this resource is not a file, it will return an empty string.
        Returns:
        String Returns either '_self' or '_blank' ('' if not a file)
